<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddb2c2507-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06" identifier="/us/usc/t12/s285"><num value="285">§ 285.</num><heading> Nonvoting stock</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Stock not held by member banks shall not be entitled to voting power.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="iddb2c2508-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06">(<ref href="/us/act/1913-12-23/ch6/s2">Dec. 23, 1913, ch. 6, § 2</ref> (par.), <ref href="/us/stat/38/253">38 Stat. 253</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="iddb2c2509-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="iddb2c250a-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="iddb2c250b-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section is comprised of the eleventh par. of section 2 of act <date date="1913-12-23">Dec. 23, 1913</date>. For classification of other pars. of section 2 of this Act, see Codification note set out under <ref href="/us/usc/t12/s222">section 222 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
